- ðŸ›ï¸ **Sales by Product Category:** Visualize which product groups (e.g., Furniture, Technology) drive the most revenue.
- â­ **Top 10 Products by Sales:** Identify best-selling items using a ranked bar chart.
- ðŸŽ›ï¸ **Interactive Filters:** Slicers for Region, Month, and Product Category allow dynamic exploration of data.

